OL,3,C'My mouldy council flat landed me in
OL,4,Chospital'
OL,6,FA man who claims his mould-infested
OL,7,Fflat landed him in hospital says the
OL,8,Fcouncil has been ignoring his pleas
OL,9,Ffor help for five years.
OL,11,FEvery room in Neil Cook's one bedroom
OL,12,Fflat in Driffield is affected by
OL,13,Fmould, which covers his bathroom
OL,14,Ffloor, oven, fridge and bed sheets.
OL,16,FMr Cook, who has lived in the property
OL,17,Ffor five years, believes exposure to
OL,18,Fdamp caused him to be admitted to
OL,19,Fhospital two years ago with the blood
OL,20,Fcondition anaemia.
