OL,3,C'My mouldy council flat landed me in
OL,4,Chospital'
OL,6,FEast Riding of Yorkshire Council says
OL,7,Fit is aware of his concerns.
OL,9,FMr Cook said: "You go to bed thinking
OL,10,Fabout it and you're waking up at 2am,
OL,11,Fso you go back to bed and you get
OL,12,Firritable. Some nights I don't sleep
OL,13,Fand some nights I do but then you wake
OL,14,Fup and it's still here.
OL,16,F"You just think: who's going to
OL,17,Fbelieve me that this is not my fault?"
