OL,3,C'My mouldy council flat landed me in
OL,4,Chospital'
OL,6,FMr Cook pays almost #400 a month to
OL,7,Frent the council flat, and has been
OL,8,Flogging complaints since 2021, but
OL,9,Fclaims he has been repeatedly ignored.
OL,11,FHe says he tries to spend as little
OL,12,Ftime as he can at home during the day.
OL,14,F"People used to say to me in town 'oh
OL,15,Fwe've noticed you're in the streets a
OL,16,Flot'," he said.
OL,18,F"And then they see the place that I
OL,19,Fhave to live in. That's why. 'Would
OL,20,Fyou like to come home to this?' I say
OL,21,Fto them. And the answer is 'no'.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/5
