OL,3,C'My mouldy council flat landed me in
OL,4,Chospital'
OL,6,F"I think (the council) look at me and
OL,7,Fthey think, it's his fault. Some
OL,8,Fnights you get emotional and you just
OL,9,Fbreak down in tears."
OL,11,FAfter ITV News Calendar contacted East
OL,12,FRiding of Yorkshire Council about Mr
OL,13,FCook's flat, the authority said it has
OL,14,Fa contractor ready to step in to carry
OL,15,Fout work on the property.
OL,17,FIn a statement the council said: "We
OL,18,Ftake the concerns of our tenants very
OL,19,Fseriously and we are aware of the
OL,20,Fdisrepair concerns raised by our
OL,21,Ftenant.
