OL,6,F"We have a contractor ready to carry
OL,7,Fout the necessary works but are
OL,8,Fstruggling to have contact with our
OL,9,Ftenant to make the necessary
OL,10,Farrangements.
OL,12,F"We would urge our tenant to make
OL,13,Fcontact with the housing team so that
OL,14,Fwe can work with him to plan for the
OL,15,Fworks to his home."
